## The Short Version

Triple Whale is purpose-built for Shopify—dead-simple setup, Moby AI, and a massive community. mbuzz is platform-agnostic with server-side tracking, 8 attribution models, and custom rules. If you're Shopify-only and value simplicity, Triple Whale is built for you. If you're on any other platform, or want deeper attribution, mbuzz is the choice.

## At a Glance

| Factor | mbuzz | Triple Whale |
|--------|-------|--------------|
| Starting price | Free / $29-299/mo | $129-279/mo |
| Platforms | Any (Shopify, WooCommerce, custom) | Shopify only |
| Attribution models | 8 + custom rules | 3 |
| Tracking method | Server-side (SDKs) | Client-side (pixel) |
| AI features | No | Moby AI (Claude-powered) |
| Setup time | Days | Minutes (Shopify app) |
| Community | Growing | 40K+ Shopify brands |
| View-through attribution | Yes | No |
| LTV attribution | Yes | Basic |
| Profit tracking | Via attribution | Native dashboard |

## Where mbuzz Wins

### Platform-Agnostic

Triple Whale is Shopify-only. If you're on WooCommerce, Magento, BigCommerce, headless, or custom—Triple Whale won't work. mbuzz supports any platform through server-side SDKs for Rails, Django, Laravel, Node.js, and Shopify.

This also matters for the future: if you ever migrate off Shopify, Triple Whale becomes useless overnight. mbuzz travels with you.

### Server-Side Tracking

Triple Whale uses client-side pixels that ad blockers strip from 30-40% of sessions. mbuzz tracks events on your server—95%+ event capture regardless of browser privacy settings. For accurate attribution, the data you don't see matters as much as the data you do.

<%= render "articles/embeds/mbuzz_showcase" %>

### Model Flexibility: 8 Models vs 3

Triple Whale offers 3 basic attribution models. mbuzz offers first-touch, last-touch, linear, time-decay, U-shaped, W-shaped, Markov Chain, and Shapley Value—plus custom rules. See how credit shifts between channels under different models:

<%= render "articles/embeds/model_comparison" %>

### Custom Attribution Rules

Triple Whale has no custom attribution logic. mbuzz lets you build rules that match your business—weight by channel type, funnel stage, recency, or any combination:

<%= render "articles/embeds/dsl_editor" %>

### View-Through Attribution

Triple Whale only tracks clicks. mbuzz tracks both click-through and view-through attribution. In a world of YouTube pre-rolls, display ads, and social media impressions, click-only tracking misses the upper funnel entirely.

### Lower Entry Point

mbuzz starts free. Triple Whale starts at $129/mo. If you're evaluating attribution tools without budget commitment, mbuzz lets you explore all 8 models at no cost.

## Where Triple Whale Wins

### Shopify Setup: Minutes, Not Days

Triple Whale installs as a Shopify app. Literally minutes to first data. mbuzz requires SDK integration—straightforward for developers but not instant. For non-technical Shopify store owners, this is a real differentiator.

### Moby AI (Claude-Powered)

Triple Whale's Moby AI lets you ask questions in natural language: "What was my best campaign last week?" "Which products have the highest margin?" mbuzz shows you data across 8 models—but you interpret it yourself. For operators who want answers, not models, Moby is compelling.

### Massive Shopify Community

40K+ Shopify brands use Triple Whale. That's a massive community for benchmarking, tips, and support. mbuzz's community is growing but can't match this scale yet.

### E-Commerce-Native UX

Triple Whale's interface is designed for e-commerce operators—profit dashboards, product analytics, creative performance. mbuzz is a more general attribution tool that serves multiple business types.

### Profit Tracking Dashboard

Triple Whale's native profit tracking—seeing true P&L by channel after COGS, shipping, and ad spend—is built for DTC operators who think in margin, not attribution credit.

## The Pricing Reality

| Scenario | mbuzz | Triple Whale |
|----------|-------|--------------|
| Getting started | Free | $129/mo |
| Growing store | $29-99/mo | $129-279/mo |
| Scaling store | $299/mo | $279/mo+ |

At lower tiers, mbuzz is cheaper with more attribution depth. At higher tiers, pricing converges—but mbuzz includes 8 models and custom rules that Triple Whale doesn't offer at any price.

## Choose Triple Whale If...

- You're Shopify-only and always will be
- Dead-simple setup (minutes) is priority #1
- You want Moby AI for natural-language data queries
- You value a large community of Shopify brands
- Profit tracking dashboards matter more than model flexibility
- Your team is non-technical

## Choose mbuzz If...

- You're on WooCommerce, Magento, custom, or multi-platform
- You want 8 attribution models + custom rules
- Server-side tracking accuracy matters (95%+ event capture)
- View-through attribution is important for your media mix
- You might leave Shopify someday
- Budget is a factor (free tier, $29 starting)

## The Verdict

**Triple Whale** is the right choice for Shopify-only stores run by non-technical teams who value simplicity, community, and AI assistance over attribution depth. It's purpose-built for Shopify operators and it shows.

**mbuzz** is the right choice for teams on any platform (including Shopify) who want deeper attribution—8 models, custom rules, server-side tracking, view-through. It works where Triple Whale can't and offers more model flexibility where they overlap.

The deciding question: are you Shopify-only and want simple? Triple Whale. Are you multi-platform or want deep attribution? mbuzz.

